sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant KeyManager
    participant Storage

    User->>App: Send message/media
    App->>KeyManager: Generate encryption key
    KeyManager-->>App: Return encryption key
    App->>App: Encrypt message/media with key
    App->>Storage: Store encrypted message/media
    Storage-->>App: Confirm storage

    User->>App: Request message/media
    App->>Storage: Retrieve encrypted message/media
    Storage-->>App: Return encrypted message/media
    App->>KeyManager: Retrieve decryption key
    KeyManager-->>App: Return decryption key
    App->>App: Decrypt message/media with key
    App-->>User: Deliver decrypted message/media

    Note over User, App: Key rotation and verification processes occur periodically
    KeyManager->>KeyManager: Rotate encryption keys
    KeyManager->>Storage: Update stored keys
    KeyManager-->>App: Confirm key rotation